quran[14]{c,v,t}:
  19,12,"Ya yahya khuthialkitaba biquwwatin waataynahu alhukmasabiyya"
  19,13,"Wahananan min ladunnawazakatan wakana taqiyya"
  19,14,"Wabarran biwalidayhi walam yakun jabbaranAAasiyya"
  19,15,"Wasalamun AAalayhi yawma wulidawayawma yamootu wayawma yubAAathu hayya"
  19,16,"Wathkur fee alkitabimaryama ithi intabathat min ahliha makanansharqiyya"
  19,17,"Fattakhathat min doonihim hijabanfaarsalna ilayha roohanafatamaththala laha basharan sawiyya"
  19,18,"Qalat innee aAAoothu birrahmaniminka in kunta taqiyya"
  19,19,"Qala innama ana rasoolurabbiki li-ahaba laki ghulaman zakiyya"
  19,20,"Qalat anna yakoonu lee ghulamunwalam yamsasnee basharun walam aku baghiyya"
  19,21,"Qala kathaliki qalarabbuki huwa AAalayya hayyinun walinajAAalahu ayatan linnasiwarahmatan minna wakana amran maqdiyya"
  19,22,"Fahamalat-hu fantabathatbihi makanan qasiyya"
  19,23,"Faajaaha almakhadu ilajithAAi annakhlati qalat ya laytaneemittu qabla hatha wakuntu nasyan mansiyya"
  19,24,"Fanadaha min tahtihaalla tahzanee qad jaAAala rabbuki tahtakisariyya"
  19,25,"Wahuzzee ilayki bijithAAi annakhlatitusaqit AAalayki rutaban janiyya"
